Tung Sahur Clicker: Keep Clicking to Unlock Surprises!

Tung Sahur Clicker is a unique clicker game where all the fun and excitement come from nonstop clicking. Players interact directly with the main character, and each click brings valuable coins. The more coins you collect, the better the rewards, unlocking endless upgrades and challenges.

This game is not just about clicking—it’s also a journey of discovery: unlock support items, change your character’s look with special skins, customize the in-game weather, and most importantly, compete to get your name on the leaderboard. Start clicking, collect coins, unlock upgrades, and race for the top rank with your friends!

Player tasks and goals

Click to earn coins

  • Your main task is to click on the character to collect coins.
  • The faster you click, the more coins you get, unlocking endless upgrade opportunities.

Unlock support items

  • Use coins to buy special items that boost your clicking power.
  • These items help increase speed and give you more coins with every click.

Collect character skins

  • Unlock many unique skins to transform your character’s look in fun and creative ways.

Discover weather skins

  • The game world changes with exciting weather skins, making each play session feel fresh.

Compete on the leaderboard

  • The higher your score, the better your rank.
  • Show your clicking skills and persistence against many other players.

Game control

  • Use the mouse to click on the character.
  • Spend coins to unlock upgrades and items.
  • Test your finger speed and patience to reach the highest achievements.
